It’s emerged that OR Tambo District Municipality Executive Mayor Nomakhosazana Meth’s two sons have been killed in a car crash. They died on Friday evening in the Mthatha area. Their passing is particularly painful for the Meth family as the two young men had just successfully completed their matric and were to take up studies at tertiary level. The Eastern Cape Government has conveyed its condolences and sympathy to Mayor Meth and her family.